album.title: King Of The Delta Blues Singers

wiki.content:
The Robert johnson, born May 8th 1911, died aug 15, 1938 ,early blues guitarist only cut  two studio sessions in his life and managed to record only 29 tracks in all.
 
 but despite this he become a legend in his time, this is where the real blues comes from, and dont you forget it! listen to his track (cross roads) please,,,,,,
 
 Treat yourselves and discover the real blues, happy hunting,,,,,,,,
